reviewText: great music video Ringgo star ronnie woods  and many more ,

In this movie no body plays any instrument. The music is taken from the cd "Willie and the Poor Boys" (which I like very much) and the musicians pretend to play. I did not see Jimmy Page anywhere and some times some of the musicians pretend to play in songs where they do not appear in the original cd. It is a fun movie, but I thought, before I bought it, that they played for real. For this reason I find more interesting the back stage film. 0n the sleeve they do not mention these facts, and they make you think the musicians play for real.
Buena musica, virtuosos instrumentistas, very good, con estos dioses del rock and roll no se podia esperar nada mejor, corto y preciso.
I had this concert on VHS, It finally came out on DVD (NTSC). I bought it, I enjoy it.
